data.title: "ZERO EGO" JOGGERS
data.description:
Soft, streamlined joggers that carry a wink of self-aware style. These joggers are for people who can laugh at themselves while still looking effortlessly put together — the kind who wear subtle luxury without shouting. The tapered cut and thoughtful rise make them sit confidently whether you’re lounging at home, grabbing coffee between errands, or layering for a late-night city walk. The fabric feels substantial yet smooth against the skin, and it holds up wash after wash so the embroidered details stay crisp. Wear them with a slouchy tee for low-key mornings or pair with an elevated hoodie for a casual night out. These joggers blend comfort and attitude: quietly refined, slightly ironic, and undeniably wearable.

Product features
- 60% cotton / 40% polyester blend — smooth, strong, embroidery-friendly
- Pre-shrunk fleece for consistent fit after washing
- Medium-heavy fabric weight (7.2 oz/yd² / 244 g/m²) for durability and structure
- Tapered fit with lower front rise and longer back rise for comfortable, flattering wear
- Blank sourced from El Salvador or Honduras

Care instructions
- Machine wash: cold (max 30C or 90F)
- Do not dryclean
- Iron, steam or dry: low heat
- Tumble dry: low heat
- Non-chlorine: bleach as needed

data.title: "LOWKEY" CAP
data.description:
This trucker cap brings dry humor and confident ease to every outfit. Lightweight mesh keeps the head cool while the hard-buckram front holds its shape, so the embroidered logo or bold statement sits sharp and readable. Walk into a coffee line or a late-night gig and let the cap do the talking — it says you can laugh at trends while still caring about quality. The precurved Permacurv® visor and matching undervisor shield your eyes without looking try-hard. An adjustable snap closure and mid-profile fit make it comfortable for all-day wear, and the stitched detailing and branded sticker on the visor give it that elevated, streetwise finish. This is for people who layer irony over craftsmanship and call it style.

Product features
- Structured mid-profile six-panel cap with hard buckram front panels
- 60% cotton/40% polyester front and visor; 100% polyester mesh back for breathability
- Precurved Permacurv® visor with matching undervisor and eight rows of stitching
- Adjustable plastic snap closure and comfortable 100% cotton sweatband
- Branded details: visor sticker and sewn-in Yupoong label; meets safety/compliance standards

Care instructions
- Use warm water and dish soap and clean spots off your hat. It's not necessary to soak the whole item. For hard to clean spots use a soft bristled brush.

data.title: "HUMBLE  ELITE" TEE
data.description:
A lightweight moisture-wicking tee that wears like a confident smirk. The cut sits clean and modern, letting the fabric move with you while keeping things dry and breathable. The DTF logo reads like a private joke—subtle, ironic, and sharply placed—so you can step into a coffee shop, a rooftop party, or an afternoon of city wandering and feel quietly self-assured. The extra-light polyester keeps the silhouette crisp without cling. Small details — a self-fabric collar, side seams, and double-stitched hems — give it structure that lasts, while the tear-away label keeps the neck comfortable. For people who enjoy low-key swagger and a little sartorial wit, this tee fits right into days that call for effortless polish and a wink.

Product features
- 100% polyester: durable, shape-retaining, quick-drying.
- Extra-light fabric (3.8 oz/yd²): breathable, barely-there feel.
- Construction details: side seams and double-needle hems for structure and longevity.
- DTF print: sharp, durable graphic transfer with clean edges.
- Comfort touches: self-fabric collar and tear-away label for a smooth fit.

Care instructions
- Machine wash: cold (max 30C or 90F)
- Do not bleach
- Do not tumble dry
- Do not iron
- Do not dryclean

data.title: "SELF MADE (WITH HELP)" HOODIE
data.description:
This hoodie is for the person who walks into a room with a smirk and knows exactly how to wear irony like a designer accessory. Thick, structured fabric feels substantial against the body, while the oversized cut drapes with intentional ease — like you borrowed someone else’s confidence and made it yours. The double-layer hood adds warmth and presence without the clutter of drawstrings. Small details — ribbed cuffs and waistband that spring back into place, double-needle seams, and a tear-away label — keep the silhouette clean and long-lasting. Slip it on for late-night city walks, low-key gallery openings, or days when you want to look composed while quietly saying, “I don’t care, but I do.”

Product features
- Double-layer hood (no drawstring) for clean warmth and styling
- Stretchy 1x1 ribbed cuffs and waistband that retain their shape
- Durable double-needle stitching on all seams
- Soft yet substantial 80% cotton / 20% polyester heavy fabric (10 oz / yd²)
- Oversized fit with tear-away label for comfort and a polished look

Care instructions
- Machine wash: cold (max 30C or 90F), gentle cycle
- Non-chlorine: bleach as needed
- Tumble dry: low heat
- Iron, steam or dry: low heat
- Do not dryclean

data.title: THC LOGO TEE
data.description:
This T-shirt is for the person who wears irony like an accessory. Soft, lightweight cotton drapes just right while an elevated cut keeps the silhouette clean. Slip it on for a dry, knowing smile—whether you’re grabbing coffee, tagging along to a gallery opening, or lounging with friends who appreciate a sharp joke. The tone is quietly confident: you don’t announce it, but the shirt does the talking. It sits comfortably through conversations that pivot between earnest and absurd, and it pairs as easily with worn-in jeans as with a crisp blazer when you want to lean into contrast. Bring it to low-key nights out, casual creative meetups, or lazy afternoons at home; it holds its shape and keeps that lived-in look without losing polish.

Product features
- 100% combed and ring-spun cotton for a smooth, strong feel
- Lightweight fabric (4.3 oz/yd²) for breathable everyday wear
- Side seams and shoulder tape for longer-lasting shape and fit
- Double-needle hems for reinforced durability at sleeves and bottom

data.title: "EFFORTLESSLY MODEST" CREWNECK
data.description:
This long sleeve crewneck tee brings a sly wink to everyday style. It’s made for people who enjoy irony and quiet confidence — the ones who can joke about needing validation while still dressing with intention. The fabric feels soft and light against the skin, and the elevated cut keeps the silhouette clean and modern. Wear it layered under a jacket for city nights or alone on a cool morning. It’s the kind of staple that reads effortlessly curated: laid-back, a little tongue-in-cheek, and undeniably well-made. The subtle details — neat side seams, reinforced hems, and shoulder tape — give it a tailored feel that holds up through repeat wear. For those who appreciate quality and humor in equal measure, this tee slides seamlessly into the wardrobe and the conversation.

Product features
- 100% combed ring-spun cotton (varies by color) — soft, smooth hand-feel
- Lightweight 5.6 oz fabric for comfortable all-day wear
- Side seams and shoulder tape for lasting shape and fit
- Double-needle stitching on sleeves and hem for durability
- Classic fit with tear-away label for clean, irritation-free wear

Care instructions

- Do not bleach

data.title: "I'M NOT BRAGGING" PREMIUM HOODIE
data.description:
Too Humble Couture Hoodie slips on like a joke only the wearer fully appreciates — confident, ironic, and quietly luxurious. The thick, 10 oz fabric and fleece-lined hood wrap you in warmth and substance; seams reinforced with split-stitch double-needle sewing promise durability that matches the attitude. The relaxed cut lets it layer over anything while ribbed cuffs and waistband keep the silhouette neat. It’s for people who enjoy cultural nods and deadpan humor, who choose an $85 hoodie not for flash but for the understated statement it makes. Wear it to late-night gatherings, gallery openings, or slow weekends when you want comfort that reads like intention.

Product features
- Plush fleece-lined hood for extra warmth
- Heavy 10 oz fabric for substantial feel and durability
- Relaxed fit suitable for layering
- Ribbed-knit cuffs and waistband for secure fit
- Tear-away label for tag-free comfort

Care instructions
- Machine wash: cold (max 30C or 90F), gentle cycle
- Do not bleach
- Tumble dry: low heat

data.title: "OBVIOUSLY\ HUMBLE" OVERSIZED TEE
data.description:
Too Humble Couture speaks to the confident, ironic dresser — the person who can smirk at trends while somehow elevating them. This oversized boxy tee wraps you in soft, mid-weight cotton that holds its shape and shows off an effortless, relaxed silhouette. Dropped shoulders and a roomy cut make it easy to layer or wear alone, while the double-stitched hems and quality ring-spun fibers mean it will age like a favorite found piece. Wear it to coffee shop hangs, late-night gallery walks, or while casually flexing that dry sense of humor — it reads like an inside joke the moment you step into a room.

Product features
- 100% airlume combed and ring-spun cotton for softness and smooth print surface
- Dropped shoulders for a relaxed, boxy silhouette

data.description:

This hat is ideal for adults looking to elevate their casual outfits and add a touch of personality to their look. Perfect for gifting on birthdays, holidays, and special occasions.
